1.0.name: wordpress/rtpanel-hooks-editor
1.0.description:
This plugin is add-on for rtPanel Theme Framework and should be used alongwith it.

It adds an option page under rtPanel Theme Options, using which, a user can write codes for various action and/or filter hooks supported by rtPanel Theme Framework

Using this plugin a user need not edit any theme files to achieve desired functionality.

Useful Links

  • rtPanel Hooks Editor Plugin's Homepage
  • Hooks Reference
  • Free Support Forum
